_:N170bf60cb5d94a29b766f20de7ea01d7 <http://schema.org/description> "The South Downs National Park (SDNP) authority conserves and enhances the natural beauty, wildlife and cultural heritage of the South Downs and promotes opportunities for the understanding and enjoyment of the area by the public. SDNP works with the Department for Environment, Food & Rural Affairs ." .
